      • compress

        UndoRedoAction compress(UndoRedoAction nextUndoRedo)
        Try compress to one undo/redo action.
        If the compression fail, null is return.
        This is call when we reach the undo/redo limit. Before discard first action if we can't gain more place on compression
        Parameters:
        nextUndoRedo - Next action try to compress with
        Returns:
        A compress undo/redo or null if the two actions can't be compress together
